        </div>

        <div class="card me-3 p-1 border-0">
            <div class="row g-0">
                <div class="col-md-4 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
                    <img src="/static/images/artists.png"
                         class="card-img rounded-start d-none d-sm-block" alt="">
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-8">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title" style="font-weight: 700 !important;">Әншілер үшін</h5>
                        <p class="card-text" style="font-weight: 700 !important;">Музыкалар каталогы пен профильдерге
